[32m+[m[32m## 🔐 **P1: CORE SECURITY HARDENING**[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### **What it Does:**[m
[32m+[m[32m- **HTTP-only Cookies:** Prevents XSS token theft[m
[32m+[m[32m- **CSRF Protection:** Validates all state-changing requests[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Security Headers:** HSTS, CSP, Frame protection[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Rate Limiting:** Global and endpoint-specific limits[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Input Validation:** Comprehensive Zod-based validation[m
[32m+[m[32m- **File Upload Security:** Magic byte validation and content scanning[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m### **Console Logs Explained:**[m
[32m+[m[32m```[m
